    <item>
      <title>苏纳克与斯塔默首次辩论之际，奈杰尔·法拉奇全力投入英国竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/nigel-farage-barrels-into-uk-election-campaign-as-sunak-faces-first-starmer-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奈杰尔·法拉奇的批评者称他为“无耻的机会主义者”。周一，这位脱欧设计者选择了一个完美的时机给里希·苏纳克一记重拳——英国大选首场电视辩论的前一天，而一项重要民意调查显示，首相领导的执政党保守党将遭遇历史性溃败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/nigel-farage-barrels-into-uk-election-campaign-as-sunak-faces-first-starmer-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹副总统访问俄罗斯，商讨武器换港口协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sudan-s-deputy-visits-russia-with-weapons-for-port-deal-on-table</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹副领导人正在前往俄罗斯进行会谈，几天前，这个北非国家的军队表示，如果俄罗斯允许克里姆林宫在红海沿岸建立军用加油站，苏丹可能会获得武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sudan-s-deputy-visits-russia-with-weapons-for-port-deal-on-table</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:43:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将大幅削减庇护申请数量 严厉打击移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/biden-to-crack-down-on-migrant-flows-by-slashing-asylum-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将于周二签署一项行政命令，允许他暂停在美墨边境的一些庇护申请，以期遏制移民越境并解决他在与唐纳德·特朗普的竞选活动中面临的最大问题之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/biden-to-crack-down-on-migrant-flows-by-slashing-asylum-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:36:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利警告称美国大选将威胁热门宏观交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/morgan-stanley-warns-us-elections-threaten-popular-macro-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利表示，由于投资者争相削减风险敞口，美国大选不确定性加剧可能会危及今年一些最受欢迎的宏观交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/morgan-stanley-warns-us-elections-threaten-popular-macro-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谢因鲍姆盟友在墨西哥国会以微弱优势错失绝对多数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sheinbaum-allies-narrowly-miss-supermajority-in-mexico-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当选总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆领导的联盟几乎赢得了国会的绝对多数，获得了众议院三分之二的席位和参议院近三分之二的席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sheinbaum-allies-narrowly-miss-supermajority-in-mexico-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:04:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙将收紧签证规定以应对创纪录的移民数量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/portugal-to-tighten-visa-rules-in-response-to-record-immigration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙政府计划收紧移民规则，要求大多数希望进入和居住在该国的外国人必须持有工作签证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/portugal-to-tighten-visa-rules-in-response-to-record-immigration</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 17:55:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法拉奇加入竞选后，苏纳克可能对人权公约采取强硬立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sunak-mulls-move-on-echr-as-farage-plunges-uk-tories-into-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 正在考虑加强其保守党在《欧洲人权公约》上的立场，因为灾难性的民意调查和英国脱欧顾问奈杰尔·法拉奇 (Nigel Farage) 决定在大选中代表改革英国参选，使得首相的执政党面临被彻底击败的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sunak-mulls-move-on-echr-as-farage-plunges-uk-tories-into-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 17:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威军事首脑认为增强北约防御的能力已所剩无几</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/norway-chief-of-defense-eirik-kristoffersen-sees-short-window-to-boost-nato</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威国防部长表示，在俄罗斯重建发动常规袭击的能力之前，北约有两到三年的时间来准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/norway-chief-of-defense-eirik-kristoffersen-sees-short-window-to-boost-nato</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 16:47:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非非国大必须穿越雷区才能保住权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-elections-anc-has-to-navigate-minefield-to-retain-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非非洲人国民大会在上周的选举中遭遇历史性挫败，自 1994 年种族隔离制度结束后上台执政以来首次失去议会多数席位。现在，该党仅获得 40.2% 的选票，被迫寻求结盟或联合执政——很可能与其最大的政治对手结盟。讨价还价才刚刚开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-elections-anc-has-to-navigate-minefield-to-retain-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 16:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西前财政部长称卢拉政府曾联系他，希望他能担任巴西石化公司的职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/former-brazil-finance-head-says-he-was-contacted-for-braskem-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西前财政部长吉多·曼特加 (Guido Mantega) 表示，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 的政府希望他能进入巴西石化公司 (Braskem SA) 董事会，如果股东批准，他将接受这份工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/former-brazil-finance-head-says-he-was-contacted-for-braskem-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 16:33:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
